These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, white, red
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes red is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | ebony | white | red   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, baccarat, havana
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Cigar      | baccarat | alhambra     | havana      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, bike
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Transport       | bus     | helicopter | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, old-henry
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Cigar   | old-henry | montecristo | aristoff     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
House: cape-cod, colonial, ranch-style
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the ranch-style house##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| House         | colonial | cape-cod     | ranch-style |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, chinese
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the chinese is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Nationality        | chinese | japanese      | pakistani  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

