.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, orange, blue
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Color           | apricot | blue | orange |

