.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, peach, pomegranate
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person eating peach is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Transport   | snowmobile     | tram | bus |

