.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, country, hip-hop
1. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the fan of country is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | chess  |
| Music-Genre     | hip-hop     | punk      | country |

