.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, aconite
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Flower      | begonia   | zinnia    | aconite    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | adventure | zombie |

