.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
City: san-francisco, paris, venice
1. the fan of trance is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| City   | venice    | san-francisco | paris |

