.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, punk, folk
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, social-worker
1. the journalist is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | folk   | punk     |
| Job    | social-worker | journalist | dressmaker |

