.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
City: prague, liverpool, berlin
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| City      | prague  | berlin | liverpool  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

