2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | woodworking | rock-climbing    |
| Job        | coach    | pilot | lawyer |

