.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pepper, spinach
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, rose
1. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | spinach | cherry       | pepper  |
| Flower   | rose  | orchid | daffodil |

 